title: Arrival #1
author: Princess Andrea
pages: Oh, what a dreadful day! 😱 I've awakened in a land. 🌍 Where are my servants?!
It appears I'm expected to fend for myself! How barbaric! 🏰✋ How does one survive without royal aid?
I must learn quickly... Is that a punch tree? 🌳👊 Seems so unladylike. But alas, necessity calls!
